The total saving is really tiny. The minimum size of such repack is 28.9 GB. But there is a bright sight too – it installs in mere 8-10 minutes from HDD to HDD. So, here’s my poll. russian-movies-weekend-26/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #26
russian-movies-weekend-26/.description: I know, I know, it’s been a while. But all those new games keeping falling and lack of properly subtitled/voiceovered Russian movies online… this all is making this “series” harder and harder…

russian-movies-weekend-25/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #25
russian-movies-weekend-25/.description: Long time no see, товарищи! After a two months hiatus your lovely RMW returns, with a vengeance!

russian-movies-weekend-24/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #24
russian-movies-weekend-24/.description: Today we’re going into adventure. Actually, two of them. In the first movie (co-production of USSR and Italy) you will see how Italians were trying to find treasure in a Soviet Russia. And in the second animation movie you will look at the Russian vision of J.R. Kipling’s “The Jungle Book”.

russian-movies-weekend-19/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #19
russian-movies-weekend-19/.description: Another two perfect examples of Russian/Soviet culture. I think that our vision of Winnie-the-Pooh is much better, than Disney’s one. And as for “Office Romance”… well, I love it. Almost all movies by Eldar Ryazanov are masterpieces, but this one is very warm personally for me. Feel free to share if it will touch you too.

russian-movies-weekend-16/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #16
russian-movies-weekend-16/.description: This week I present you two favorite flicks of my husband.

russian-movies-weekend-14/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #14
russian-movies-weekend-14/.description: The first movie of this week is one of my favorites. The only problem for foreign people will be understanding of all idioms and accents of people in it, but the humor is pretty international.

russian-movies-weekend-13/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #13
russian-movies-weekend-13/.description: This week you should see those two masterpieces of the Soviet comedy genre, which are still aired up to this date on every major TV channel at least twice a year.

russian-movies-weekend-12/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #12
russian-movies-weekend-12/.description: This week I present you the Oscar-winning movie and the most popular animated series in Russia.

russian-movies-weekend-10/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #10
russian-movies-weekend-10/.description: Another week – another Russian movies to see.

russian-movies-9/.title: Russian Movies #9
russian-movies-9/.description: This week we’ll go with Russian traditional festives: vodka, bears and balalaikas.

russian-movies-weekend-8/.title: Russian Movies Weekend #8
russian-movies-weekend-8/.description: Another week, another Russian movies mini-pack.
